{"tid":155033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毒霧還有這功能？ 中國學者：減少水污染","createTime":"2017-03-13T17:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T03:46:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1791c339930b36320328bdf58527b7b2a36e4c38","tid":155033,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"2017-03-13  23:22<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpQ1Uy27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpQ1Uy27.jpg&h=68fe73d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">中國學者研究發現，毒霧減弱了黃土高原的夏季季風，進一步減少被雨水沖進河裡、湖裡的土壤，最後減緩優養化水污染。圖為被毒霧籠罩的上海。（資料照，法新社）</span><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國霾害嚴重引發關注，有中國學者研究發現，毒霧減弱了黃土高原的夏季季風，進一步減少被雨水沖進河裡、湖裡的土壤，最後減緩優養化水污染。<br />\n《中國網》報導，中國蘭州大學西部環境教育部重點實驗室主任陳發虎，本月初發表在國際期刊《自然氣候變化》的報告指出，霧霾間接減緩了優養化水污染，因此，為了對抗毒霧減少空氣中的懸浮微粒，可能會導致黃土高原上的季風增強，造成水質優養化加劇、藻類蔓延，嚴重破壞水中生態系統。<br />\n陳發虎說，1000多年來，黃土高原面臨強烈夏季季風和水質優養化問題，「過去50年來，工廠和汽車排放的懸浮微粒扭轉了這些自然現象」。夏季季風的強度受到海陸溫差影響，差異越大，季風越強。陳發虎表示，空氣中增加的懸浮微粒成了遮擋太陽輻射的保護傘，漸緩地面增溫，降低海陸溫度差異進而減弱了季風。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳發虎的研究指出，懸浮微粒減少造成水質優養化，會造成數十億元的經濟損失，對該地區淡水資源造成嚴重威脅。他說，「這是很麻煩的，因為它表明人類的行為已改變了氣候，就算消除了損害，後果可能還是存在」。<br />\n陳發虎也補充，這項研究的目的並不是為了促進毒霧，而是在警告官員，注意減少排放造成的潛在副作用，並制定更全面的防霾計畫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2003023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2003023&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0ae8643f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2003023&h=d313d472\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2003023</a>"},{"pid":"f05f8382cd5ab62d8c45ef851ca3ede57ec398cb","tid":155033,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來水污染係因為泥沙"},{"pid":"298476e2b7eaae20c4b4700200518b00786049ba","tid":155033,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:17:08.000Z","msg":"中國學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed9d0b6bc9667866274c43ee7880403b8f10875","tid":155033,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"其實係特登整出黎嘅環保噴霧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e79e2ee3845c8c8dc9e1b3d9e6629c7896bafe8","tid":155033,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:25:08.000Z","msg":"本末倒置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e178bd2707a7d02713f2de26de782d6def995eb","tid":155033,"uid":4209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T19:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來水污染係因為泥沙</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e79e8f41838146f80b4bbfade02134642e6fd0","tid":155033,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep